          <h1 class="jumbotron-heading">About Me</h1>
          <p class="lead text-muted">
            Hello! My name is Abel Teklemariam, and I am a second-year software engineering student. I am passionate about technology and have always been 
            fascinated by how software can make a positive impact in people's lives. I have built a solid foundation in computer science principles, algorithms,
